  <brief_title>Effect of Prematurity on Renal Function in 5 Years Old Children</brief_title>
  <acronym>SUIVIREIN</acronym>
  <official_title>Effect of Prematurity on Renal Function in 5 Years Old Children Comparison of Former Premature Children Treated by Ibuprofen in the Neonatal Period to Controls</official_title>
